    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 12 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 1 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 11</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You move slow but steady, emulating the thrashing attacks of a wild bear. You take a -2 penalty to Defense, but gain a +2 bonus to grapple checks and a +1 bonus to unarmed attack damage. All melee attack rolls are modified by Strength (if they weren't already).</p>\n\n\n\n",
